00:17:07.410 --> 00:17:08.610
Publishers.

00:17:08.820 --> 00:17:11.640
So there are a lot of
different publishers,

00:17:11.640 --> 00:17:16.170
and a lot of them have different
levels of involvement as to whether

00:17:16.210 --> 00:17:18.110
or not they pick up your product.

00:17:18.190 --> 00:17:21.810
Some of them want to be involved in
actual development of the product

00:17:21.900 --> 00:17:24.080
and finishing the product along.

00:17:24.090 --> 00:17:27.020
Others want to be involved in packaging.

00:17:27.270 --> 00:17:30.020
Some are taking a very
active role in the marketing.

00:17:30.080 --> 00:17:33.360
But some of them don't do any of that.

00:17:33.400 --> 00:17:35.630
They really are acting
more like a distributor,

00:17:35.810 --> 00:17:39.460
and it's just an easier method of entry
if you're having difficulty working with

00:17:39.460 --> 00:17:45.170
one of the distributors and you want to
get into a retail channel more quickly.

00:17:45.330 --> 00:17:46.270
So it can vary.

00:17:46.280 --> 00:17:50.000
And there are publishers that
work through distributors,

00:17:50.020 --> 00:17:52.700
and there are publishers who are direct.

00:17:52.750 --> 00:17:54.700
So there's no definite.

00:17:54.700 --> 00:18:00.560
A good example of a publisher is Aspire,
who does all the EA games,

00:18:00.560 --> 00:18:04.860
and they pick up smaller titles.

00:18:04.890 --> 00:18:06.770
I don't know if any of you
are familiar with iSale,

00:18:06.780 --> 00:18:10.680
which is a new product that
helps you sell products on eBay,

00:18:10.860 --> 00:18:14.160
but they're working through Aspire.

00:18:14.490 --> 00:18:20.820
And Aspire is currently with Navarre,
and so that's how Apple Retail procures,

00:18:20.820 --> 00:18:21.860
say, iSale.

00:18:21.860 --> 00:18:24.590
It goes through the publisher,
through the distributor,

00:18:24.690 --> 00:18:28.200
and then to the retailer.

00:18:28.220 --> 00:18:30.880
And the third general
category are vendor reps.

00:18:30.940 --> 00:18:34.130
